                     PERSONAL NIGHTMARE SOLUTION

Typed by ???  Edited by PARASITE.


   JUST A FEW NOTES:-
   THE WORDS IN SIDE THE "   " `s ARE THE WORDS THAT NEED TO BE ENTERED AT
   THE REQUIRED TIMES.IT IS ADVISABLE THAT YOU SAVE THE GAME REGULARY AS
   THERE ARE QUITE A FEW WAYS TO DIE.N,S,E & W STAND FOR NORTH,SOUTH ETC..

DAT 1
   N,E
   WAIT UNTIL JIMMY BLANDFORD IS RUN DOWN
   "EXAMINE JIMMY BLANDFORD"
   CLICK `ROOM'
   DRAW IN ALL OF THE OBJECTS INTO YOUR INVENTORY
   W,S
   "EXAMINE HEAVY JACKET"
   PULL KEY INTO INV
   N,E,E,E,E,E,E,E,E,E,S
   "UNLOCK DOOR","OPEN DOOR",S
   OPEN S DOOR
   S,W
   "LOOK UNDER TABLE"
   E,S,W
   "LOOK BEHIND PAINT POTS"
   CLICK `ROOM'
   PULL OILSTONE,SLEDGEHAMMER & SECATEURS INTO INV
   CLICK ON LARGE BOX
   PULL MAUL INTO INV
   E,N,N,N,N,N,W,W,S,W
   "UNLOCK DOOR","OPEN DOOR"
   S
   "DIAL 1815 INTO SAFE"
   "LOOKIN SAFE"
   CLICK ON PAPERS
   CLICK `ROOM'
   PULL CERTIFICATE INTO INV
   N,N,W,W,W,N
   "OPEN DOOR"
   N,N,N
   "HIT DRAWER WITH HAMMER"
   "LOOKIN DRAWER"
   PULL KEY INTO INV
   S,S,S,W,W
   "LOOKIN WEEDS"
   "GET GARLIC"
   N,N
   "UNLOCK DOOR"
   "OPEN DOOR"
   N
   "HIT WALL WITH HAMMER"
   "HIT WALL WITH HAMMER"
   "HIT WALL WITH HAMMER"
   "EXAMINE WOMAN"
   "CUT FINGERS WITH SECATEURS"
   CLICK `ROOM'
   CLICK ON PRAYER BOOK
   UP
   OPEN W DOOR
   W
   "EXAMINE BOOKS"
   CLICK `ROOM'
   CLICK ON TREASURE ISLAND BOOK
   PULL SAVINGS BOOK INTO INV
   E,DOWN
   OPEN S DOOR
   S
   "EXAMINE SMALL CHAIR"
   "GET WOOL"
   N,E,S,S,DOWN
   OPEN E DOOR
   E,E,E,E,E
   OPEN E DOOR
   E
   "DROP SHOES"
   UP,N
   "EXAMINE ALICE"
   "GET KEY"
   "LOOK UNDER BED"
   S
   "DROP STEPLADDERS"
   "GO UP STEPLADDERS"
   "OPEN LOFT DOOR"
   UP
   "GET JUG"
   "FILL JUG WITH WATER"
   "POUR WATER ON SUIT"
   "UNLOCK JUDY"
   "DROP BRASS KEY"
   DOWN,DOWN
   "GET SHOES"
   S,S,W,W,W,W,W,W,W,W,W,W
   "OPEN GATES"
   N
   "EXAMINE FENCE"
   "GET STAKE"
   N
   TYPE "KILL DOG WITH STAKE" PRESS RETURN WHEN THE DOG GETS CLOSE
   N,N
   "SWING OVER HOLE"
   UP
   OPEN N DOOR
   N
   "EXAMINE JACKET"
   PULL BOTTLE INTO INV
   S,DOWN
   "SWING OVER HOLE"
   S,S,S,S,S,E,E,E,E
   UNLOCK S DOOR
   OPEN S DOOR
   S
   OPEN E DOOR
   E,UP,E
   OPEN NE DOOR
   NE
   "OPEN WARDROBE"
   PUT THE FOLLOWING IN WARDROBE:-
   YALE + SHINY KEYS,STAKE,TIE & PYJAMAS
   "CLOSE WARDROBE"
   SW,W,DOWN,W
   "GET BUGLE"
   SW
   "PUT PLUG IN HOLE"
   "LOOKIN WASHING MACHINE"
   CLICK ON TROUSERS
   PULL KEY INTO INV
   NE
   "REMOVE HANDLE FROM MAUL"
   "DROP MAUL HEAD"
   E,UP,E,NE
   "SLEEP"

DAY 2
   SW
   CLOSE NE DOOR
   OPEN N DOOR
   N
   "GET MIRROR"
   S,W
   OPEN N DOOR
   N
   "EXAMINE PILLOW"
   "GET DIARY"
   "UNLOCK DIARY"
   S,DOWN,W
   OPEN N DOOR
   N,N,E,E,E,E,S,E,E,E
   "GIVE DIARY TO POLICEMAN"
   "GIVE NUMBERPLATE TO POLICEMAN"
   "GIVE CERTIFICATE TO POLICEMAN"
   "DROP CERTIFICATE"
   W,W,W,S
   "LOOKIN BIN"
   PULL NUMBERPLATE INTO INV
   N,E,E,E
   "GIVE NUMBERPLATE TO POLICEMAN"
   S
   "GIVE SAVINGS BOOK TO POSTMISTRESS"
   "BUY STAMP"
   "EXAMINE DISPLAY STAND"
   PULL ENVELOPE INTO INV
   "PUT FILM IN ENVELOPE"
   "PUT VOUCHER IN ENVELOPE"
   "PUT STAMP ON ENVELOPE"
   "ADDRESS ENVELOPE"
   N
   "PUT ENVELOPE IN POST BOX"
   W,W,W,N,W,N,W,W,DOWN
   OPEN E DOOR
   E,E,E,E,E
   AS SOON AS THE VAMPIRE APPEARS
   W,W,W,W,
   "REFLECT LIGHT WITH MIRROR"
   W,UP,E,E,S,W,W,W,S,S
   WAIT UNTIL AFTER MIDNIGHT
   OPEN N DOOR
   N
   WHEN CAR IS CHASING YOU IF YOU CONTINUE TO GO NORTH AND EAST IT WILL
   EVENTUALLY HIT A TREE.
   N
   "OPEN GLOVE BOX"
   "LOOKIN GLOVE BOX"
   PULL KEYS INTO INV
   S,W,W,W,W,W,S,S,E,UP,E,NE
   "SLEEP"

