   "PRAY"
   "PUT TEARS IN BOTTLE"
   "PUT CORK IN BOTTLE"
   W,S,S,S,E,S,S
   UNLOCK S DOOR
   OPEN S DOOR
   S,E
   "EXAMINE PAPERS"
   "TAKE BILL"
